# Dockerignore override for the phantom-stack build.
# The project ships no .dockerignore; exclude local caches/artifacts so they
# don't bloat the build context or leak into the image. Source, tests, configs
# are all kept since the SDK is installed in editable/dev mode.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
.git
.venv
.mypy_cache
.pytest_cache
.ruff_cache
build/
dist/
.coverage*
.audio_cache/
